With regard to
 Tables (ref) \& (ref), 
 LLM-augmented SEs could bring
 precise answers for more complex queries
 into the realm of feasibility,
 most notably, for information needs on planning or advice, and also perhaps for analytical queries.
 Note, however, that efficiency may be a showstopper. More research is needed on how to balance the adequacy of responses and the necessary computational resources.